<br />

<br />
If you look at most zones they run you through a little zig zag with very boring textures so they only had to maintain one simple texture in two adjacent zones.  The zones with very spacious zonelines all have very similar textures in both zones and mostly just change the fauna.  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
Like I said.... just speculation.  Losing a texture might allow them a NPC model or two more or let them do some funky shadow or water stuff.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
